headline: COR's MWI Animal Health to Merge With Covetrus in $3.5 Billion Deal
summary: Cencora is set to merge MWI Animal Health with Covetrus in a $3.5B deal, retaining a 34.3% stake as it unlocks capital and targets animal health growth.
